item.title: About
item.description: Hello There My name is Daniel Jackson I am a software engineer with an interest in economics Writing blog to reinforce what I learn. Studied Computer Science and Applied Math Economics The point of this blog is for self-betterment, not advertisement so I’ll leave the about me section at this. Feel free to reach out to me on Github or email Shotout to the creator of the Hugo Theme used as a template for this blog, Razon Yang .
